description: IDVO is an ETF of high-quality international large and mid-cap companies through American Depositary Receipts (ADRs) with a history of dividend and earnings growth, along with a tactical covered call strategy on individual securities. Capital Wealth Planning LLC (CWP) and Seymour Asset Management LLC serve as investment sub-advisers to the Fund.
name: Amplify CWP International Enhanced Dividend Income ETF
